# Gamepad Tester Online (HTML5 Gamepad API)

A lightweight open-source JavaScript gamepad tester using the HTML5 Gamepad API.
Test Xbox, PlayStation, and generic controllers directly in your browser.

## Features

* Detect connected gamepads
* Button press detection
* Analog stick visualization
* Trigger pressure values
* Vibration support detection
* Works in Chrome, Edge, Firefox

## Live Demo

Use the full featured version here:
👉 https://mygamepadtester.com

## Basic Usage

```html
<script src="gamepad.js"></script>
```

```js
window.addEventListener("gamepadconnected", (e) => {
  console.log("Gamepad connected:", e.gamepad);
});
```

## Supported Controllers

* Xbox Series X/S controller
* PS5 DualSense
* PS4 DualShock
* Nintendo Switch Pro
* Generic USB gamepads

## Why this project exists

This is a simplified open-source version of the full testing suite available at:
https://mygamepadtester.com

The full version includes:

* Deadzone tester
* Input lag tester
* Stick drift test
* Trigger test
* Vibration test
* Multi-controller support

